<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="A" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Arched" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Arched,</orth> 1) built with an arch: <cit><quote>the gates of monarchs are a. so high,</quote> <bibl n="shak. cym 3.3.5" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. III, 3, 5</bibl></cit>.<lb />2) bent like an arch: <cit><quote>the right a. beauty of the brow,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 3.3.59" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. III, 3, 59</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>his a. brows,</quote> <bibl n="shak. aww 1.1.105" default="NO" valid="yes">All's I, 1, 105</bibl></cit>.
